Title: Bountiful Beetles
Description:
General Anub'azal has great plans in motion for the swarmery, Rak-Ush. He intends to return it to working order, to support his war campaign.

However... I have my reservations about the two he left in charge. 

Kish'nal seems to have a good head on his shoulders, but Vix'aron? Volatile is an understatement. They may require some... prodding.

Seek out Kish'nal at Rak-Ush and follow up on Anub'azal's orders.
RewardText: Ah, so the general has sent out an observer?
